        <a class="area-pill" href="/greater-darwin/">All of Greater Darwin</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Found live termites? Don&rsquo;t touch them &mdash; call now.</h2>
        <p>Tell us you have active termites and we prioritise your inspection. Species ID, extent, and a clear plan &mdash; urban Darwin or rural Litchfield.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Request urgent inspection</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
